17
00:00:43,690 --> 00:00:47,050
Well, China is great at using people to make
an example.

18
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:50,590
He Jiankui says he edited the DNA of the twin
girls

19
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:52,390
