24
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:10,409
It works by making a cut in the DNA to disable
a specific gene.”

25
00:01:10,409 --> 00:01:12,869
Now his claim has not been independently verified,

26
00:01:12,869 --> 00:01:16,430
so we don’t know for a fact Dr. He did what
he says he did.

27
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:19,770
But even so, it’s created a huge controversy.

28
00:01:19,770 --> 00:01:22,189
Gene editing is banned in many countries.

29
00:01:22,189 --> 00:01:23,189
Guess what?

30
00:01:23,189 --> 00:01:24,529
Not in China.

31
00:01:24,529 --> 00:01:26,960
The reasons most countries ban it are:

32
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,960
One,

33
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,659
this is a totally new frontier

34
