are getting involved.

60
00:02:33,540 --> 00:02:36,160
“China’s National Health Commission late
on Monday

61
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:40,740
ordered officials to ‘seriously investigate
and verify’ He’s claims.

62
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:43,000
Shenzhen’s Health and Family Planning commission

63
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,020
